headline: Red Robin (RRGB) Surpasses Q1 Earnings and Revenue Estimates
summary: Red Robin (RRGB) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of 133.33% and 1.28%, respectively, for the quarter ended March 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: IBD Stock Of The Day Positioned To 'Substantially Absorb' Trump Tariffs; Eyes Buy Point
summary: Cheesecake Factory stock, amid an 11% rally since Q1 earnings, traded near a traditional buy point in Thursday's stock market.
